---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Jagadeesh Thiruveedula | Senior Data Architect">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 dark:from-slate-900 dark:to-slate-800">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              Senior Data Architect
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Leading enterprise data transformation with 9+ years of expertise in GCP, GenAI, and Vector Databases. 
              Specializing in scalable data architectures that unlock business value through intelligent automation and AI-driven insights.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jthiruveedula" 
                 class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                LinkedIn Profile
              </a>
              <a href="mailto:jagadeesh.thiruveedula@outlook.com" 
                 class="px-6 py-3 border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
                Contact
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Current Role</span>
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Senior Data Architect</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Location</span>
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Dallas, TX</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Experience</span>
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">9+ Years</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Specialization</span>
                  <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">GCP & GenAI</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Expertise -->
    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-800/50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
          Core Expertise
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
              Google Cloud Platform
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Expert in BigQuery, Dataflow, Cloud Functions, and GCP AI/ML services. 
              Certified in designing enterprise-scale data architectures on GCP.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
              Generative AI & LLMs
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Building production GenAI applications with Vertex AI, implementing RAG architectures, 
              and developing AI-powered analytics solutions for enterprise use cases.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
              Vector Databases & Search
            </h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              Implementing semantic search and similarity matching using Pinecone, Weaviate, and 
              Google Cloud Vertex AI Vector Search for advanced AI applications.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Impact Statistics -->
    <section class="py-16 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
          Impact & Achievements
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">$25M+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Cost Optimization Delivered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-2">100TB+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Data Processed Daily</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-2">15+</div>
            <div class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Enterprise Projects</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 mb-2">99.8%</div>
            <div class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">System Uptime</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Professional Summary -->
    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-12">
          Professional Summary
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            As a Senior Data Architect with 9+ years of experience, I specialize in designing and implementing 
            enterprise-scale data solutions on Google Cloud Platform. My expertise encompasses the full spectrum 
            of modern data engineering, from traditional data warehousing to cutting-edge generative AI applications.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            I have successfully led data transformation initiatives for Fortune 500 companies, delivering solutions 
            that process hundreds of terabytes of data daily while reducing operational costs by millions. My approach 
            combines deep technical expertise in GCP services with strategic business acumen to ensure data architectures 
            drive measurable business value.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Currently focused on the intersection of traditional data engineering and artificial intelligence, I'm building 
            next-generation platforms that leverage vector databases, large language models, and real-time analytics to 
            unlock unprecedented possibilities for enterprise intelligence and automation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8">
          Let's Connect
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Interested in discussing data architecture, AI implementations, or potential collaborations? 
          I'd love to connect and explore opportunities.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jthiruveedula" 
             class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors font-semibold">
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:jagadeesh.thiruveedula@outlook.com" 
             class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-slate-300 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors font-semibold">
            Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
